main event: An unidentified flying object was observed at Whiteman Air Force Base, Missouri, on August 7, 1965.
interesting points: The object was bright white in color and estimated to be approximately 30-40 feet in diameter, It hovered for about 2 minutes before rapidly ascending and disappearing from view, Witnesses included at least one Security Patrolman and other personnel on the base, No photographs were taken of the object, although it was visible to multiple observers during the time of the sighting.
